definitions.definition: ( slang , humorous , derogatory ) Synonym of gay : a homosexual man .
( slang , humorous , derogatory ) Term of address to any man or boy .
( slang , humorous , derogatory ) An effeminate or insufficiently masculine man or boy.
examples: That bloke's got a pink t-shirt on - what a gaylord !
